  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<strong>Oracle Volcano Mystery Power</strong><br/><br/><p>Whenever a creature fails a saving throw against one of your spells that deals fire damage, that creature catches on fire, taking 1 point of fire damage per spell level at the beginning of its turn. The fire lasts for 1d4 rounds, but it can be extinguished as a move action if the creature succeeds at a Reflex save (using the original spell's DC). Dousing the creature with water as a standard action grants a +2 bonus on this save, while immersing the creature in water extinguishes the fire. Spells that don't grant a saving throw don't cause a creature to catch on fire.</p>",
